About the game:
"cars" is simple car racing game.
Each map has two turns.
You can edit maps with Gimp.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Howto compile:
Requires:
SDL, SDL-devel, SDL_mixer, SDL_mixer-devel

cd cars
make

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Howto run:
cd cars
./cars

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
player1
	left, right, up, down
player2
	a, d, w, s
player3
	j, l, i, k
player4
	KP_4, KP_8, KP_5, KP_6
	
ESC............	skip map 


